data.description: Come check out this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom house in a great community in Buckeye. The house features an open floor plan with a spacious family room, vaulted ceilings, and tile flooring throughout. The master bedroom offers a full bath with separate shower, tub and a large walk-in closet. You'll also enjoy a low maintenance back yard with a nice patio, artificial grass and pavers. Don't miss out on this remarkable property! ***Seller to credit the buyer up to 2% towards a rate buy down or concessions.
